==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trader
<hw>Trad"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
engaged in trade or commerce; one who makes a business of buying and
selling or of barter; a merchant; a trafficker; <as>as, a
<ex>trader</ex> to the East Indies; a country
<ex>trader</ex>.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A vessel engaged in the coasting or foreign
trade.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tradescantia</ent>⟦br⟧
\'d8
